description:
<!--StartFragment-->

Eagles Wings Productions Sensational artiste Alvy on her sophomore project lavishes praises on the all Mighty God as she says Thank you for everything which he has done, is doing and will do. Thanking the most high God is a culture, often neglected by many Christians despite the emphasis placed on thanksgiving in the book of Psalms. Set on a dance tune produced by Cypiano Alvy will make you dance and give Jesus all the Thank you he rightfully deserves.
